{"tid":137473,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"告東尼細女：冇全心奉獻唔會成功","createTime":"2017-02-28T00:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T07:17:50.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"132c678f4335dcd69d38654b5290d7067d683824","tid":137473,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:00:03.000Z","msg":"「爹哋幾惡，佢做老闆要strong，個團隊請最好嘅人，唔會浪費時間做錯嘅事，我都試過，同事做唔到，會叫人搵過第二啲嘢做，要嚴格啲，唔好浪費時間。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：梁錦雯<br />\n錄影：李祉澄<br />\n場地：Ursus Fitness<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036933_9468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036933_9468.jpg&h=d26fb176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n告東尼工作認真，連阿女Antonia都佩服，話學唔足爸爸嘅鬥心。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036934_32de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036934_32de.jpg&h=d22a100a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一家人關係親密，以往會結伴騎馬，o依家愛打golf。（受訪者提供圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036935_5ec3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036935_5ec3.jpg&h=4be90975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（受訪者提供圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036937_5962.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036937_5962.jpg&h=7cf2de5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036938_9f96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036938_9f96.jpg&h=42748543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036940_51fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036940_51fc.jpg&h=9c45801d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAntonia現職運動平台，想學爸爸咁工作認真。（攝影：林德雄、郭賢興）<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170226/56354576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170226%2F56354576&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F17IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e6c72b41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170226%2F56354576&h=c2609bdd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170226/56354576</a>"},{"pid":"fa54b7f98621e86cfdbb64b2c8b241b572f3dd61","tid":137473,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:01:18.000Z","msg":"&hellip;"},{"pid":"ca0ae82f276750c5df2cb5568c619cc4ec939126","tid":137473,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:17:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7ead17c205564d11a0767268f008560427e7ed0","tid":137473,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T20:08:15.000Z","msg":"唔知佢騎功點呢"},{"pid":"98ac0354b900aeafccded1ff4c804d4388c28fcb","tid":137473,"uid":1781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T20:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知佢騎功點呢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd812b32c22def7bb52ddb391807217416028daf","tid":137473,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T23:45:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>同過維珍老細打網球　告東尼細女試玩滑浪板瑜伽</strong><br />\n<br />\n告東尼細女Antonia嘅Ig，充滿唔少做運動靚相，當中包括同維珍集團主席Richard Branson打網球、同鯊魚游水等等，絕對係位好動分子。<br />\n<br />\n採訪當日，現職GuavaPass運動平台嘅Antonia，走訪兩個合作夥伴嘅studio玩瑜伽、舉重、打拳，連休息時間都要開Apps，揀定下星期去另一個城市玩咩運動，佢笑言喺唔同國家上過各種課程：「我試過最瘋狂一個月玩咗10次，當中除咗gym、瑜伽運動，成日都會去發掘玩新運動，好似最近玩過一個有聲音治療嘅Gong Bath、有康復治療嘅跳床Bounce，同喺滑浪板上面做瑜伽。」有冇諗過介紹父母嘗試新類型運動，Antonia笑言會帶媽媽參加一啲冥想相關運動，而爸爸就要做多啲肌肉伸展運動。<br />\n<br />\n提到一家人最愛嘅共同運動，Antonia話細個會跟爸爸、哥哥騎馬，o依家一家人鍾意打高爾夫球，但佢球技就最差：「以前細嗰冇興趣，幫佢哋拎球棍，佢哋鼓勵我打，o依家成日仲有keep住一齊打golf，我打一個鐘都OK，要打4個鐘好多個洞，就會冇晒專注力，冇乜興趣。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：梁錦雯<br />\n攝錄：李祉澄<br />\n場地：Odinson、Ursus Fitness  <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036980_38f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036980_38f2.jpg&h=3b9c03e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAntonia熱愛運動，周遊列國期間都要報名上堂做gym，更加試過同維珍集團主席Richard Branson打網球（）。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036982_30ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036982_30ce.jpg&h=5d6349ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAntonia嘅ig好多旅遊相，當中都搵到好多戶外活動相。（instagram圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036983_e281.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036983_e281.jpg&h=35607586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打網球唔特別，同Richard Branson就包你未試過。（instagram圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036984_004b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036984_004b.jpg&h=7892d5b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受旁當日，Antonia去過兩間合作機構上堂，玩舉重、打拳同瑜伽。（攝影：林德雄、郭賢興）<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036986_9c4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036986_9c4a.jpg&h=bf2f64d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺香港就做室內瑜伽，Antonia話喺外地玩過其他玩意，好似係滑浪板上面做瑜伽咁。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036987_45ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036987_45ab.jpg&h=ab6d0585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488036989_040c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488036989_040c.jpg&h=a7134422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAntonia連休息時間都要上GuavaPass報定堂。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170226/56354578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170226%2F56354578&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F17IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d212a8b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170226%2F56354578&h=22bfecee\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170226/56354578</a>"},{"pid":"fa712dc7fc04eb2a89d16e8dc5beca1102b006f2","tid":137473,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:17:50.000Z","msg":"波路唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}